Idents(obj.opossum.gabaergic) <- "RNA_snn_res.1.1"

cells.pv <- WhichCells(obj.opossum.gabaergic, ident = c("1", "4", "6", "7", "8", "9", "14"))
obj.opossum.gabaergic$subclass <- ifelse(colnames(obj.opossum.gabaergic) %in% cells.pv, "Pvalb", "ambiguous")

cells.sst <- WhichCells(obj.opossum.gabaergic, ident = c("2", "5", "11", "12", "15", "17"))
obj.opossum.gabaergic$subclass[cells.sst] <- "Sst"

cells.vip <- WhichCells(obj.opossum.gabaergic, ident = c("3", "13", "16"))
obj.opossum.gabaergic$subclass[cells.vip] <- "Vip"

cells.lamp5 <- WhichCells(obj.opossum.gabaergic, ident = c("10", "18"))
